a1, a2 and it has n columns,
so it looks like that.

00:06:03.300 --> 00:06:06.950
That's what our matrix
A looks like.

00:06:06.950 --> 00:06:10.000
So we're saying if you take this
product, you have to be

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:13.360
able to reach any guy,
any member of Rm.

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:15.710
Well, what does this product
look like if where taking this

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:17.280
product instead of writing
an x there, I could

00:06:17.280 --> 00:06:19.070
write x like this.

00:06:19.070 --> 00:06:23.480
x1, x2, all the way to xn.

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:27.770
So this product is going to be
