00:06:44.340 --> 00:06:45.900
That's what this product is.

00:06:45.900 --> 00:06:50.320
And in order for T to be onto,
this combination has to be

00:06:50.320 --> 00:06:53.040
equal to any vector in Rm.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:54.130
Well, what does this mean?

